        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The air conditioning system expansion valve has been revised for optimized performance. When
                    installing the new improved expansion valve in place of the old style expansion valve, it is also
                    necessary to replace the air conditioning relay or modify the air conditioning clutch wiring circuit
                    for optimum performance.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>The air conditioning relay replacement or air conditioning clutch wiring circuit
                            modification is NOT required if the vehicle is equipped with APADS (Air Conditioning
                            Protection and Diagnostics System).
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
